{
  "stem": "17374.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that hurts me, because I got the feeling that is-- I'm different.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my parents, especially my mother, when she was alive, tried to be-- tried to avoid this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She tried to be similar to the other, to all the friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I have, all around me, Catholics, because Poland was Catholic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we celebrate-- and they come to Easter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They paint the eggs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my mother let me do it the same, and put in a basket.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then when the girls went to church, I went with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My mother was very tolerant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And once, I remember, for Christmas she bought a little tree, but my father was very cross.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I have to throw it away, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I have all-- I didn't really feel that [INAUDIBLE] I am something bad about that, because I was Jewish, no.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really, not till the war time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the war-- before, just before the war, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's where we are live, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived there a few months, still, when the German were there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were ordered to wear the arm band.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the first, first thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was already embarrassing, and [INAUDIBLE] on the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was so many different orders.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every few weeks was something different that you don't-- you don't allow to go on the street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to, not on the foot, but you have to walk here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then you're not allowed to be after 8 o'clock or 9 o'clock or something like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We have to be home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So many different ordering every day, every few days And then we went--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "German, there were German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And actually, not, not directly German-- straightaway, they make a police, or they make somebody Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they made Jewish policemen.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
